OL,5, A Russian diplomat has quit his job in 
OL,6, protest at the "bloody, witless" war   
OL,7, "unleashed by Putin against Ukraine".  
OL,9,FBoris Bondarev, whose LinkedIn says he 
OL,10,Fworked at the Russian mission to the UN
OL,11,Fin Geneva, told the BBC he knew his    
OL,12,Fdecision to speak out may mean the     
OL,13,FKremlin now considers him a traitor.   
OL,15,FBut he stood by his statement which    
OL,16,Fdescribed the war as "a crime against  
OL,17,Fthe Ukrainian people" and "the people  
OL,18,Fof Russia".                            
OL,20,FMoscow has not yet commented.          
